<i>noun</i>: 카운슬링 [], 상담 [상담] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>카운슬링 []</dt><br>
<dd>counseling</dd><br>
<dd>고민이나 심리적인 문제를 해결하기 위해 전문적으로 도움을 주고 받는 활동.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of giving or receiving professional help, to remove a worry or to solve a psychological problem.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>상담 [상담]</dt><br>
<dd>consultation; counseling</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 문제를 해결하기 위하여 서로 이야기함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of talking to one another to solve a certain problem.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>